  "prompt": "How can I reach Pune from Mumbai?",
  "response": "Reaching Pune from Mumbai is quite convenient due to the well-connected transportation network between the two cities. Here are the main options:\n\n### 1. **By Train**  \n   - **Mumbai to Pune trains**: There are frequent trains between Mumbai and Pune, including:  \n     - **Intercity Express**  \n     - **Deccan Queen**  \n     - **Indrayani Express**  \n     - **Sinhagad Express**  \n   - **Duration**: ~2.5 to 3.5 hours depending on the train.  \n   - **Departure Stations in Mumbai**: Mumbai CST, Dadar, or Lokmanya Tilak Terminus (LTT).  \n   - **Arrival Station in Pune**: Pune Junction.  \n   - **Booking**: Tickets can be booked via the IRCTC website or app.  \n\n### 2. **By Bus**  \n   - **MSRTC (State Transport) buses**: Affordable and frequent buses from Mumbai to Pune.  \n   - **Private Volvo buses**: Comfortable and faster options available from various operators.  \n   - **Departure Points in Mumbai**: Dadar, Borivali, Thane, or Mumbai Central.  \n   - **Duration**: ~3 to 4 hours depending on traffic.  \n   - **Booking**: Tickets can be booked online through RedBus, Abhibus, or directly from operators.  \n\n### 3. **By Flight**  \n   - **Mumbai (BOM) to Pune (PNQ) flights**: Multiple daily flights by airlines like IndiGo, Air India, and SpiceJet.  \n   - **Duration**: ~1 hour flight time.  \n   - **Airport Transfer**: Pune Airport is about 10 km from the city center.  \n   - **Note**: This option is less common due to the short distance and longer transfer times to/from airports.  \n\n### 4. **By Car**  \n   - **Route**: Take the Mumbai-Pune Expressway (NH48), one of the best highways in India.  \n   - **Distance**: ~150 km.  \n   - **Duration**: ~2.5 to 3.5 hours depending on traffic.  \n   - **Toll**: There are tolls on the expressway.  \n\n### 5. **By Taxi or Cab**  \n   - **Ola/Uber** or private cab services offer convenient door-to-door options.  \n   - **Cost**: Higher than buses or trains but comfortable.  \n\nChoose the option that best suits your budget, time, and comfort preferences!",
